data.description: Welcome to your dream abode! This stunning, sun-drenched, 3-bed, 2-bath sanctuary is an architectural masterpiece, boasting high vaulted ceilings that create an airy and spacious atmosphere. Nestled on an expansive lot, this gem is a haven for those who crave privacy and tranquility. Indulge in the luxury of upgraded bathrooms, exquisitely designed with modern fixtures and sleek tiling. Feel the warmth under your feet with the elegant laminate flooring that adds an element of contemporary charm to each room. Illuminate your world with the ambiance created by the recessed lighting, creating the perfect setting for relaxation and entertainment. Unwind in the grandeur of a master bedroom that includes a generous walk-in closet, offering ample space for your cherished wardrobe. The state-of-the-art stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen beckon the inner chef in you to create culinary delights, while the kitchen island becomes the heart of your home, perfect for hosting gatherings and making memories. Admire the craftsmanship of the beautiful cabinetry that adorns the home, adding a touch of sophistication and practicality to every corner. Enjoy the spacious backyard that invites you to indulge in outdoor activities, create a picturesque garden, or simply bask in the serenity of nature. This is not just a house; it's a statement of luxury living. Seize the opportunity to make this yours and elevate your lifestyle to new heights. Contact us today to experience this oasis firsthand! Property has solar! Seller is willing to give credit towards rate buy down. 4.75% rate buy down!
